hrag">Chung Tinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%E1%BB%91c-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u-Lu%C3%A2n/poem-YorXSjO-Q8X4wyE_Ywou2g">Khốc Vương Bành Châu Luân - 哭王彭州掄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%A2y-c%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-HOPcSGxn2KpqwthVoNdZkg">Tây các kỳ 1 - 西閣其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-k%C3%ADnh/poem-4_cG8gJHlklsmrDWSimGqA">Thạch kính - 石鏡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tung-cao-5/poem-WDtysUXnUli_Q1a8vZyvWw">Tung cao 5 - 崧高 5</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br></div>	</div>
